languages.text: "Тебе придется, элантах. Иначе выбор сделаю я. И он тебе не понравится".

traits.locale_text: "Тебе придется, элантах. Иначе выбор сделаю я. И он тебе не понравится".
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "You will have to, elantach, or else I will make the choice for you. And it will not be to your liking."

languages.text: 「エランタ、選ばねばならない。さもなくば、我があなたの代わりに選ぶ。望まぬ選択をすることになる」
languages.original_text: "You will have to, elantach, or else I will make the choice for you. And it will not be to your liking."

traits.locale_text: 「エランタ、選ばねばならない。さもなくば、我があなたの代わりに選ぶ。望まぬ選択をすることになる」
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: “你必须做出选择，外界人。否则我会替你做出选择，而你恐怕不会喜欢我的选择。”
languages.original_text: "You will have to, elantach, or else I will make the choice for you. And it will not be to your liking."

traits.locale_text: “你必须做出选择，外界人。否则我会替你做出选择，而你恐怕不会喜欢我的选择。”
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: « Il le faut, elantach, ou je choisirai pour vous. Et ça risque de ne pas vous plaire. »
languages.original_text: "You will have to, elantach, or else I will make the choice for you. And it will not be to your liking."

traits.locale_text: « Il le faut, elantach, ou je choisirai pour vous. Et ça risque de ne pas vous plaire. »
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: «Tendrás que hacerlo, elantach, porque si no, seré yo quien tome la decisión. Y no te va a gustar».
languages.original_text: "You will have to, elantach, or else I will make the choice for you. And it will not be to your liking."

traits.locale_text: «Tendrás que hacerlo, elantach, porque si no, seré yo quien tome la decisión. Y no te va a gustar».
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Ihr werdet es müssen, Elantach, sonst treffe ich die Wahl für Euch. Und sie wird Euch nicht gefallen."
languages.original_text: "You will have to, elantach, or else I will make the choice for you. And it will not be to your liking."

traits.locale_text: "Ihr werdet es müssen, Elantach, sonst treffe ich die Wahl für Euch. Und sie wird Euch nicht gefallen."
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Buna mecbursun elantach. Sen yapmazsan ben yapacağım. Seçimimi beğeneceğini de sanmam."
languages.original_text: "You will have to, elantach, or else I will make the choice for you. And it will not be to your liking."

traits.locale_text: "Buna mecbursun elantach. Sen bir seçim yapmazsan, ben yapacağım. Seçimimi beğeneceğini de sanmam."
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion
